TEST STEPS

1. Open class1, class2 editors;
2. Press Ctrl + E - make sure that opened editors list appeared, containing class1 and class2;
3. Create new file;
4.  Press Ctrl + E - make sure new file is listed in opened editors list;
5. Select class1 - make sure its editor is now active. 
